{"tid":1718131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑衣青年墮樓亡    陶輝帶隊到場","createTime":"2019-11-13T18:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:55:30.000Z","uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd44c098f8b2e6837126e343192cc8c6fd4c36db","tid":1718131,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"【0232 荃灣】黑衣青年墮樓亡    陶輝帶隊到場<br />\n<br />\n周三（13日）晚上，一名黑衣黑褲青年倒臥在葵涌勝耀街嘉里物流中心對出位置，地面有大片血跡，他被送院後證實死亡。有目擊者稱他是從高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n凌晨，署理新界南總區指揮官陶輝帶同防暴及速龍警員，到嘉里物流中心一帶視察。<br />\n<br />\nfrom 立場"},{"pid":"6304c7b9aa261f38b91f556b22d0bbc48a1c54fc","tid":1718131,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:47:44.000Z","msg":"想消滅證據？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9ee82869e6d77e82ac3c4e9f4efca012ce1b2f","tid":1718131,"uid":73856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:48:42.000Z","msg":"洗地"},{"pid":"6d8b5aa436a46b78c9f49a18db550c2f61089453","tid":1718131,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:49:50.000Z","msg":"咁重視？殺咗人驚有另一個周同學？要曬附近啲cam先？"},{"pid":"71898b9ae384ae1842612a6b0dc2eb3c36b8d823","tid":1718131,"uid":113902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"其實佢署任左好耐總區指揮官 正任個指揮官去左邊<br />\n佢總警司人工做助理處長既野 咁搵笨都做咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f31f0a58e484df9fe504582ba6efac88a58963","tid":1718131,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"拉大隊拎cctv<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n___________________________________<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>「請廣傳」香港黑警濫權資料庫 (中英日語）</ins></span></strong><br />\n依個網手足籌劃左好一段時間, 包含大量核彈, 請各位出分力廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港警察濫權實錄資料庫<br />\nH.K. Police Violence Database<br />\n香港警察暴行の事件簿</span><br />\n中文<br />\n<a href=\